data.description: This lovely home is located in the highly desirable 55+ community of Willow Gate, close & convenient to everything! It features a 2022 roof, newer 2023 appliances, new screens on the lanai in 2021, and a 2019 hot water heater. There is luxury vinyl plank flooring in the living room, with tile in all other rooms. The eat-in kitchen comes with wood cabinets, granite counters, tile backsplash, pantry, breakfast bar & plantation shutters. This split plan also features a bonus room, which is perfect for an office or den, and a two-car garage. The screened lanai overlooks the private backyard with oak trees, and the brick paver patio is great for entertaining. The community's low HOA fee includes lawn care, clubhouse with activities & swimming pool.
